flowRoot.flowPara: I love a good story. Storytelling is one of primary ways humans connect to one another. My passion is using technology to tell stories through pleasing visuals, punctual prose and interesting interactions.

Welcome! My name is Corrine Nightingale and I'm a web designer and developer based in the Portland Metro Area. I have a passion for reinventing stories, experiences and passions through digital media. Please keep scrolling to learn more about my experience in the field.
